{"id":162106,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/中国鬼城的最新谷歌卫星照片集/","date":"2011-06-17T21:30:03Z","modified":"2011-06-17T22:42:38Z","title":"中国鬼城的最新谷歌卫星照片集","content":"<p>原作者：<br />\n来源<a href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/chinese-ghost-cities-2011-5\">Satellite Pictures Of Chinese Ghost Cities</a><br />\n译者<a href=\"http://space.yeeyan.org/u/136746\">zzard</a></p>\n<p>（外媒称）中国计划在未来的20年里每年件20个城市。未知的问题是中国正在寻找买家来购买这些数量庞大的房屋。</p>\n<p>塔洛克说：“中国建了更多的房屋，中国比任何工业国家消费的钢铁、铁和水泥都要多。这些部分流向了不会有利润的高铁，还有部分则流向了没人驾驶的公路和没人居住的城市。”</p>\n<p>他还说：“这就好像步行在摩天大楼的森林，但是这些高楼都是空的。”</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617080606_78044.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>CHENGGONG正在建设数量庞大的摩天大楼。（来源：世界银行【下同】）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617080631_30937.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>CHENGGONG已经建设10万座空置的公寓。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617080652_72291.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>CHENGGONG还有两座大学，不过它们看起来还都是空荡荡的。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617080638_25400.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>JIANGSU蓬勃的新房地产开发区。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617080601_54538.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>JIANGSU外圈崭新的空房。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617080620_91428.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>JIANGSU外圈另一个房地产开发区。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617080639_47955.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>QIANDAOHU旁的奢华湖畔公寓已经被投机商买下，但却没人居住。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617080602_37402.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>CHANHSHA的城市面积是洛杉矶的2倍，但是还在向东西扩张。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617080626_89440.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>这是CHANGSHA一个庞大的房地产开发项目。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617080650_29735.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>最著名的鬼城-ORDOS，早已鬼了多年。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617090619_32877.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>ORDOS的空房。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617090653_42155.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>ORDOS更多的空房。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617090630_52102.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>在ORDOS没有汽车，除了这些停在迷人政府大楼旁的。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617090651_29131.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>中国正在ZHENGZHOU新区建造两个金融中心和15座大学。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617090621_33867.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>ZHENGZHOU新区到处都是迷人的公共大楼。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617090601_17412.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>ERENHOT被建在Inner Mongolia的一个沙漠中心。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617090611_93310.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\nERENHOT一半是空的，一半还未建成。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617090640_59552.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>ERENHOT甚至还有豪华酒店。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617090600_19469.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>能看到XINYANG东北部的橙色区域吗？</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617080631_76457.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>这么大的开发项目，连个名字都没有。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617080612_86922.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>这个城市没有汽车，除了停在政府大楼旁的这些（约100辆）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617080654_47004.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>DANTU这座城市已经鬼了超过10年了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617080632_17036.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>在DANTU的街区，没有汽车，也没有人生活的迹象。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617080658_26918.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>DANTU的一个鬼村。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617080626_56639.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>DANTU的另一个鬼村。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617080601_11802.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>BAYANNAO&#8217;ER最空的城区，那里有漂亮的市政厅和世界银行资助的水循环建筑。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-06/17/20110617080639_82762.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>最后，这张照片是超级庞大的新南中国购物中心，自从2005年开始99%都是空的。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/136746/201459#newComment\">添加新评论</a></p>\n<p><strong>相关文章：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/153856/201025?from=rss_related\">越南正在玩火</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/208397/201324?from=rss_related\">越南和中国南中国海之争的走向</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/230571/201280?from=rss_related\">中国核电站通过安全检查</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/193318/201315?from=rss_related\">中国宣传其核电站很安全</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/222029/201332?from=rss_related\">纽约时报：中国海军穿越冲绳海域 领海问题纷争四起</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/t1/524047142/yeeyan-culture/feedsky/s.gif?r=http://article.yeeyan.org/view/136746/201459\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\" method=\"POST\"> 定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n<input maxlength=\"64\" name=\"EMAIL\" size=\"25\" type=\"text\" /></p>\n<p><input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\" /> <input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\" /> <input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\" /> </form>\n","author":1,"categories":[13770,20534],"tags":[9309,10193]}